---
// Featured Article: Why Armenia
import SectionHeader from '../SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] ambient-blob bg-gold-400"></div>

    <div class="section-inner max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 relative z-10">
      <SectionHeader label="Featured" labelHy="&#1329;&#1404;&#1377;&#1398;&#1393;&#1398;&#1377;&#1409;&#1406;&#1377;&#1390;" />

      <!-- Featured Article Card -->
      <div class="gs-reveal mt-10">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gold-soft border border-gold-400/20 px-3 py-1 rounded" data-i18n data-hy="&#1350;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1337;&#1381;&#1382;&#1387;&#1405;" data-en="Investment Thesis">Investment Thesis</span>
            <span class="text-card-body-muted text-[12px] font-light">Q1 2025</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-text-primary font-semibold mb-6 leading-[1.15]">
            <span data-i18n data-hy="&#1339;&#1398;&#1401;&#1400;&#1410; &#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;: <span class='text-gold-gradient'>&#1357;&#1377;&#1392;&#1396;&#1377;&#1398;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1399;&#1400;&#1410;&#1391;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387; &#1392;&#1398;&#1377;&#1408;&#1377;&#1406;&#1400;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1384;</span>" data-en="Why Armenia: <span class='text-gold-gradient'>The Frontier Market Opportunity</span>">Why Armenia: <span class="text-gold-gradient">The Frontier Market Opportunity</span></span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-[16px] text-card-body font-light leading-[1.8] max-w-[800px]">
            <p data-i18n
               data-hy="&#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;&#1384; &#1382;&#1378;&#1377;&#1394;&#1381;&#1409;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1377;&#1399;&#1389;&#1377;&#1408;&#1392;&#1387; &#1377;&#1396;&#1381;&#1398;&#1377;&#1377;&#1408;&#1377;&#1379; &#1377;&#1395;&#1400;&#1394; &#1407;&#1398;&#1407;&#1381;&#1405;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1387;&#1409; &#1396;&#1381;&#1391;&#1384;&#1417;"
               data-en="Armenia is quietly emerging as one of the most compelling frontier market stories in the post-Soviet space. GDP growth averaged 12.6% in 2022 — the highest in Europe — driven by a technology-led boom, a surge in human capital from regional migration, and a government increasingly committed to economic modernization.">
              Armenia is quietly emerging as one of the most compelling frontier market stories in the post-Soviet space. GDP growth averaged 12.6% in 2022 — the highest in Europe — driven by a technology-led boom, a surge in human capital from regional migration, and a government increasingly committed to economic modernization.
            </p>

            <p data-i18n
               data-hy="&#1348;&#1387;&#1415;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1397;&#1398; &#1386;&#1377;&#1396;&#1377;&#1398;&#1377;&#1391;, &#1381;&#1408;&#1391;&#1408;&#1387; &#1391;&#1377;&#1402;&#1387;&#1407;&#1377;&#1388;&#1387; &#1399;&#1400;&#1410;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1396;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1382;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1377;&#1409;&#1377;&#1390;&#1417;"
               data-en="Yet the country's capital markets remain remarkably underdeveloped relative to its economic dynamism. Total assets under management across all five licensed fund managers represent a fraction of GDP — a gap that signals both structural opportunity and room for institutional growth. The Armenian Securities Exchange, recently revitalized, is seeing growing interest from both domestic and diaspora investors.">
              Yet the country's capital markets remain remarkably underdeveloped relative to its economic dynamism. Total assets under management across all five licensed fund managers represent a fraction of GDP — a gap that signals both structural opportunity and room for institutional growth. The Armenian Securities Exchange, recently revitalized, is seeing growing interest from both domestic and diaspora investors.
            </p>

            <p data-i18n
               data-hy="&#1344;&#1377;&#1407;&#1391;&#1377;&#1402;&#1381;&#1405; &#1400;&#1410;&#1399;&#1377;&#1379;&#1408;&#1377;&#1406; &#1383; &#1407;&#1381;&#1389;&#1398;&#1400;&#1388;&#1400;&#1379;&#1387;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1400;&#1388;&#1400;&#1408;&#1407;&#1387; &#1382;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1377;&#1409;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1384;&#1417; &#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1377;&#1405;&#1407;&#1377;&#1398;&#1387; &#1407;&#1381;&#1389;&#1398;&#1400;&#1388;&#1400;&#1379;&#1387;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1392;&#1377;&#1396;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1408;&#1379;&#1384; &#1377;&#1408;&#1407;&#1377;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1407;&#1377;&#1408;&#1381;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; $2.6 &#1396;&#1387;&#1388;&#1387;&#1377;&#1408;&#1380;, &#1387;&#1405;&#1391; 200+ &#1414;&#1387;&#1398;&#1407;&#1381;&#1412; &#1384;&#1398;&#1391;&#1381;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1384; &#1377;&#1395;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1381;&#1398; 25% &#1407;&#1377;&#1408;&#1381;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1377;&#1395;&#1387;&#1396;&#1400;&#1406;&#1417;"
               data-en="Particularly noteworthy is the technology sector's meteoric rise. Armenia's tech ecosystem now produces $2.6 billion in annual output, with over 200 fintech companies growing at 25% CAGR. NVIDIA has committed $500 million to AI infrastructure in the country, while ServiceTitan — founded by Armenian-Americans — became the nation's first NASDAQ unicorn with a $10B+ valuation. The country ranks 34th globally on the Fintech Index, surpassing South Korea and Spain.">
              Particularly noteworthy is the technology sector's meteoric rise. Armenia's tech ecosystem now produces $2.6 billion in annual output, with over 200 fintech companies growing at 25% CAGR. NVIDIA has committed $500 million to AI infrastructure in the country, while ServiceTitan — founded by Armenian-Americans — became the nation's first NASDAQ unicorn with a $10B+ valuation. The country ranks 34th globally on the Fintech Index, surpassing South Korea and Spain.
            </p>

            <p data-i18n
               data-hy="&#1344;&#1377;&#1397;&#1391;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1398; &#1405;&#1411;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1404;&#1412;&#1384; &#1392;&#1377;&#1398;&#1380;&#1387;&#1405;&#1377;&#1398;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396; &#1383; &#1392;&#1382;&#1400;&#1408; &#1388;&#1408;&#1377;&#1409;&#1400;&#1410;&#1409;&#1387;&#1401; &#1377;&#1394;&#1378;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1408;&#1417;"
               data-en="The Armenian diaspora — estimated at 7 to 10 million people worldwide, dwarfing the country's 3 million domestic population — represents an enormous untapped source of patient capital. With nine Forbes billionaires of Armenian origin and $1.8 billion in annual remittances contributing 14% of GDP, the diaspora's economic influence is profound. Many diaspora members maintain deep emotional and economic ties to Armenia but lack institutional-grade vehicles to channel investment back home. This is precisely the gap Algosphere was created to fill.">
              The Armenian diaspora — estimated at 7 to 10 million people worldwide, dwarfing the country's 3 million domestic population — represents an enormous untapped source of patient capital. With nine Forbes billionaires of Armenian origin and $1.8 billion in annual remittances contributing 14% of GDP, the diaspora's economic influence is profound. Many diaspora members maintain deep emotional and economic ties to Armenia but lack institutional-grade vehicles to channel investment back home. This is precisely the gap Algosphere was created to fill.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
